snippet.title: SCARLET NEXUS - DLC 3 Brain Eater Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Drop into the #SCARLETNEXUS DLC 3 "Brain Eater Pack" today to play the Karen Episode, Anime Tie-in Mission, and obtain new Costume Sets for your whole team!

Available now on Xbox and PC via Steam, and available for PlayStation users later at 9PM PST! Order: scarlet-nexus.com
